snippet.title: KINGDOM HEARTS III – Final Battle Trailer (Closed Captions)
snippet.description:
Find out more about KINGDOM HEARTS III: https://sqex.link/kingdc2b3f

Hurry and Pre-Order your KINGDOM HEARTS III Deluxe Edition before they’re all sold out! Supplies are limited! 
PS4 – https://sqex.link/kingdf431c
XB1 – https://sqex.link/kingdebd78

As unexpected events begin to unfold in the Disney worlds at the hands of the enemy's dark ambitions, the heroic trio of Sora, Donald, and Goofy find adventures ahead—from aquatic battles in the world of Pirates of the Caribbean to dances with the townspeople in the Kingdom of Corona from Tangled. 
We also get a first look at Stitch from Lilo and Stitch, a cooking-themed Ratatouille Keyblade, conversations involving Organization XIII members, and a glimpse at Kairi wielding a Keyblade!

KINGDOM HEARTS III is coming to Sony PlayStation® 4 and Microsoft Xbox One on January 29, 2019. 

Be sure to follow us to keep up to date with everything Kingdom Hearts related: 
Twitter - https://twitter.com/KingdomHearts
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/KingdomHearts
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/KingdomHearts
YouTube - https://www.youtube.com/KingdomHearts
#KingdomHearts
